==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overstand
<hw>O`ver*stand"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To stand on
the price or conditions of, so as to lose a sale; to lose by an
extravagant price or hard conditions.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What madman would <qex>o'erstand</qex> his market twice?</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overstare</ent>⟦br⟧
